  <brief_title>A Trial of the Irradiance Level of Phototherapy for Neonatal Jaundice</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Multicenter Non-inferiority Randomized Controlled Trial of the Irradiance Level of Phototherapy for Neonatal Jaundice</official_title>
